What a ride. The past two years have been a journey of personal growth and learning more about myself than I could ever imagine — there were several highs, lows, and emotions I had never felt before… But as i drove into work every day, i felt something light up inside of me… a passion I hadn’t felt before. That is how I knew I was in the right place. We couldn’t promote the show the way we wanted to because of the strike, but we did too much great work to stay silent — thank you to the incredible, talented individuals who made this all possible. Always gonna bleed purple and gold 💜💛
